    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/sgv/fbh/6044457245.html"></div>
        </div>
Popular dessert food truck looking for the right fit to expand their team!  Sweet and simple work, but very fast paced.<br>
Looking for a great team with nothing but good vibes to maintain a fun-filled working environment.<br>
<br>
<br>
Our Brand is all about QUALITY, PRESENTATION, CONSISTENCY &amp; CUSTOMER SERVICE.  <br>
If you can bring those things to the table, please continue reading!<br>
<br>
<br>
Is this job right for you?  Know what you are signing up for.. here is what to expect:<br>
  - lots of driving- must be able to drive to locations.  On the bright side, it's a new environment everyday so it will never get boring.  (gas reimbursement for far locations)<br>
  - fast paced environment- our lines get quite long, especially during the summertime.  Must be able to work well under pressure and keep positive energy<br>
  - festivals and catering- other then our daily routes, we also work festival, music festivals and cater at weddings and parties<br>
  - shifts may include nights and weekends - flexible if arranged ahead of time<br>
  - shifts range from 3-8 hours per event<br>
  - you'll be working with a team of 4 or 5 in a 16 ft space.  must work well with others, communication is key.<br>
  - must have a good hand and eye to be able to keep up with presentation and quality of the desserts.  It's pretty much an art!<br>
  - we are looking for part-time - full-time (preferably long term to grow with our company)<br>
<br>
<br>
Seeking:<br>
FOOD TRUCK DRIVER / STAFF ($12-$14 + tips depending on experience)  We will conduct training<br>
20-40 hours a week depending on your availability<br>
  - must have a valid CA driver's license<br>
  - clean driving record<br>
  - reliable transportation to and from commissary (located in Rosemead, CA)<br>
  - must be confident in driving and parking a 25 ft. fleet truck (prior experience is a plus)<br>
  - responsible for food truck set up and clean up<br>
  - will also be a part of dessert assembly<br>
** A typical day would be: drive to commissary, pick up food truck, drive to location, prep and set up truck, work on truck, clean up, drive truck back to commissary**<br>
<br>
<br>
DESSERT ASSEMBLY LINE STAFF ($11-12 + tips depending on experience)<br>
20-40 hours a week depending on your availability<br>
  - job will range from scooping ice cream, assembling and topping dessert, expediting and finishing orders, passing out orders<br>
  - our assembly line is definitely a team effort, so we are looking for a great team player<br>
  - good communication and great attitude<br>
  - must be able to work in a fast paced environment and be able to handle the pressure of long lines <br>
  - must be able to deliver good quality/instagramable and on point desserts (QUALITY, PRESENTATION, CONSISTENCY &amp; CUSTOMER SERVICE)<br>
<br>
<br>
CASHIER ($10 + tips)<br>
  - good customer service (customer's first impression starts here!)<br>
  - fun / energetic <br>
  - accuracy<br>
  - responsible for opening / closing register and making sure everything adds up<br>
<br>
<br>
Locations:<br>
2 trucks covering<br>
LOS ANGELES COUNTY<br>
ORANGE COUNTY<br>
**frequent stops include: Los Angeles, North Hollywood, Sylmar, Venice, Whittier, Fullerton, Eagle Rock, Cerritos, West LA, Monterey Park** and more...<br>
Commissary is in Rosemead, CA<br>
<br>
THE PERKS!<br>
We've had a pretty awesome history this last year.. and we love sharing our accomplishments and experience with our staff and we are always aiming to get our foot into fun events!<br>
This past year we've..<br>
  - worked an Espy's event<br>
  - had visits from Chris Paul and his family<br>
  - catered for Ray J's wedding which was televised on VH1<br>
  - catered Brandon Jenning's son's birthday party<br>
  - worked festivals such as Vans warped tour, FYF, Air + Style<br>
    complexcon<br>
  - We are also vending Coachella, Stagecoach and Hard Summer 2017<br>
    and many more to come, pretty cool!<br>
**All have been accomplished by our hardworking staff and team.<br>
<br>
If you are interested in applying, please email a brief introduction of yourself and your qualifications. Serious applicants only.<br>
PLEASE ATTACH RESUME TO EMAIL BODY.<br>
<br>
Thank you for your interest in working with our team!    </section>

